<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 1 (Ruca) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スパーダ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Spada</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルカ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ruca</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルカよォ、
マジであんなヤツの言う事聞くつもりか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, Ruca. Are you really gonna listen
to what that dude is tellin' ya to do here?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>しょうがないよ、
あの薬草は本当に貴重で
僕なんかじゃ手に入れられないんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There's nothing I can do about it. That herb is
really valuable, There's no way someone like
me would actually be able to get it on my own.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ハッ！
だからってあんなフザケた
条件呑むってェのかよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ha! So what, you're just gonna
accept their stupid ass demands?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クレス・アルベインって人を倒す……だよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have to beat someone
named Cless Alvein... right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あの成金野郎。
クレスってヤツをよっぽど
恨んでるみてぇだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That rich ass bastard. Seems to really
have a big ol' grudge on this Cless guy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>理由は教えちゃくんなかったけどよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Didn't tell us why, though.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>僕だって、こんな理由で
誰かと戦うなんて嫌だよ。
だけど今はこれしか方法がないんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't wanna fight anyone over something
like this, either. Right now though, there's
just nothing else I can do.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>野試合で一回倒すだけなら
あとで謝れば許してくれるんじゃないかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I beat him in a casual battle,
he'll forgive me if I apologize, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……たぶん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Probably.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ヘッ、どうだかなァ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heh. I wonder 'bout that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
